Defendant is before the Court for sentencing having been convicted of theft-business setting on 09-01-16.
Sentence is withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years.  Conditions of probation:
1) Pay restitution of $8,965.99 to Candlelighters of the Lakeshore Counties at a rate of $100.00 per month.  If agent determines more can be paid per month, more should be paid;
2) COMPAS assessment and follow through;
3) Full-time employment or work search as the defendant is able unless social security prohibits it;
4) No handling of funds in the course of employment, charitable groups or volunteer groups;
5) Eight (8) months Manitowoc County Jail, under the Huber Law.  Four (4) months served up front commencing 11-05-16 by 5:00 p.m., four (4) months stayed to be imposed at agent's discretion;
6) Complete 100 hours of community service in a cancer treatment center;
7) Submit a DNA sample and pay surcharge;
8) Pay costs of the action; and
9) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
Minutes.
